      @Deprecated public static NamespacedKey getKey(String key)
      Deprecated.
      Planning to remove all string based ids for recipes in the future, please use Util.getNamespacedKey(String, boolean) more information on this in the future when it's put into action
      Get a NamespacedKey from string

      If no namespace is provided, it will default to namespace in SkBee config (default = "skbee")

      Parameters:
      key - Key for new NamespacedKey, ex: "plugin:key" or "minecraft:something"
      Returns:
      New NamespacedKey
